    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rouka"
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、ちょうど良かった\n今から、葵を探しに行こうとしてたところだったんだ",
      "startTime": 3.266666611,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rouka"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "……何かあったの？",
      "startTime": 6.6278459867,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "葵に仕事の話がきてな\n今までと毛色が違うから、まずは相談しないとと思って",
      "startTime": 11.7000008345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rouka"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "君は僕達のマネージャーなんだから\nいちいち僕に相談しないで、OKしても良かったのに",
      "startTime": 18.7633798521,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rouka"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "それで、一体{user}君が\n悩むほどの仕事ってなんなの？",
      "startTime": 24.3967133126,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、前にすずがドラマにゲスト出演しただろう？\n毎週、殺人事件を解決していく……",
      "startTime": 31.5333332778,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rouka"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、あれ。僕も観たよ\n今度は僕に、あのドラマへの出演依頼がきたの？",
      "startTime": 38.2214063169,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rouka"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "それで、僕は一体何をすればいいんだい\n死体役？　スキップしながら包丁振り回すとか？",
      "startTime": 45.7547381243,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……結構やる気だな\nダンス以外の仕事は嫌がるかと思ってたんだが",
      "startTime": 52.1999968927,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rouka"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "リズノワの躍進のためにはなんでもやると言ったからね\n演技は未経験だけど、頑張ってみるよ",
      "startTime": 60.0627421459,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rouka"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "それに殺陣は一度、ちゃんとやってみたかったんだ\nいい人に教えてもらえるなら、ありがたいな",
      "startTime": 66.629408304,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rouka"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "いや……葵にやってほしいのは\n周りから交際を反対されてるカップルの役だそうだ",
      "startTime": 72.8666610162,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "いわば、ロミオとジュリエットみたいな関係だな\nそれが事件後にやっと結ばれる……って筋書きらしい",
      "startTime": 80.2793136832,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rouka"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "ロミオとジュリエット……\nつまり、恋愛がメインってこと？",
      "startTime": 87.6492536148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "ってことは、男の人と付き合う場面とか\nデートシーンなんかもあるのかな？",
      "startTime": 95.9825910171,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rouka"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "僕、デートなんてしたことも\n何をするのか考えたことも、ろくにないんだけど",
      "startTime": 101.7492576838,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rouka"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ま……まぁ、撮影では台本もあるから\nデートの内容で悩むことはない……と、思う",
      "startTime": 108.6000040133,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "それもそうか\nで、『やっと結ばれる』っていうのは、どういうこと？",
      "startTime": 114.9286439737,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rouka"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、資料の最後に書いてあったんだ\nウエディングドレスでの結婚式の撮影もあります、って",
      "startTime": 122.66667068,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "office_yuugata"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi012.m4a",
      "text": "ドラマの仕事の件、保留にしてもらって悪かったね\nリズノワのためならなんでもやると言ったばかりなのに",
      "startTime": 133.2618537347,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi013.m4a",
      "text": "あの後、莉央達にも相談してみたんだ\nあまりに無様だと、リズノワの評判にも関わるからね",
      "startTime": 140.5618527174,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi014.m4a",
      "text": "……なんだけど、莉央はドラマのことを聞くなり\n目頭を押さえて泣き始めちゃって",
      "startTime": 150.1618659417,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi015.m4a",
      "text": "「葵がお嫁に行ってしまうと想像したら、つい」\n……って。結婚式はドラマの中のことだっていうのに",
      "startTime": 157.3285315911,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi016.m4a",
      "text": "ドラマに出るだけであの様子じゃ\n僕が本当に結婚する時は、どうなるんだろ",
      "startTime": 164.3951901197,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi017.m4a",
      "text": "いや、今はまだそんな予定はないからね\nあくまで莉央が心配ってだけだよ",
      "startTime": 172.4951982577,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "それだけ葵が大事なんだろう……\nこころと愛は、なんだって？",
      "startTime": 178.8666691541,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi018.m4a",
      "text": "愛は「ウエディングドレス、似合いますよ！」って\nせっかくなんだしやればいいのにって言ってた",
      "startTime": 185.1583348592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi019.m4a",
      "text": "こころは……「葵さん、やりたくないんですか？」\n「その仕事、代わりにやりましょうか～？」",
      "startTime": 194.0250015259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi020.m4a",
      "text": "「でも葵さんより似合っちゃうかもしれませんね～」\n「って、愛ちゃんが言ってました！」……ってさ",
      "startTime": 202.3583348592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "こ、こころのやつ……",
      "startTime": 206.4916671753,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi021.m4a",
      "text": "こころはまだ子供だからね\nドレスを着て、お姫様気分にでもなってみたいんだ",
      "startTime": 211.1908137004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
